406
00:33:54,550 --> 00:33:55,440
Yitan!

407
00:34:05,670 --> 00:34:06,750
Stop, Yitan!

408
00:34:06,750 --> 00:34:08,010
What's wrong with you?

409
00:34:48,110 --> 00:34:49,800
You promised to go bird egg hunting with me,

410
00:34:49,800 --> 00:34:50,860
but you stood me up.

411
00:34:51,110 --> 00:34:52,150
Is composing couplets

412
00:34:52,150 --> 00:34:53,610
with the teacher that fun?

413
00:34:53,840 --> 00:34:56,070
