414
00:34:56,190 --> 00:34:58,520
A gentleman should be upright and proper.

415
00:34:58,590 --> 00:35:00,990
We shouldn't steal eggs from mother birds.

416
00:35:01,070 --> 00:35:01,960
Besides,

417
00:35:02,110 --> 00:35:04,920
