418
00:35:05,000 --> 00:35:05,630
You...

419
00:35:06,440 --> 00:35:08,880
Look at him! Who did he learn all this from?

420
00:35:10,320 --> 00:35:11,440
Ignore what your mother said.

421
00:35:11,440 --> 00:35:12,760
Go on, go play.

422
00:35:13,150 --> 00:35:14,280
Thank you, Daddy.

423
00:35:16,440 --> 00:35:17,640
Why'd you take a book?

424
00:35:27,840 --> 00:35:28,510
Is it sweet?

425
00:35:28,510 --> 00:35:29,030
Yes.

426
00:35:29,990 --> 00:35:31,000
So from now on,

427
00:35:31,070 --> 00:35:33,280
will you still argue with me?

428
00:35:34,150 --> 00:35:35,030
Of course not.

429
00:35:39,430 --> 00:35:40,350
Oh, right.

430
00:35:40,800 --> 00:35:42,230
Where's my little nephew?

431
