436
00:35:56,360 --> 00:35:59,160
Practicing swordsmanship in the back mountains?

437
00:36:02,710 --> 00:36:03,230
Here.

438
00:36:08,840 --> 00:36:10,570
These grapes are really sweet.

439
00:36:12,230 --> 00:36:13,150
I hope

440
