446
00:36:53,520 --> 00:36:54,630
This is not a dream.

447
00:36:56,360 --> 00:36:57,590
This is our future.

448
00:37:02,840 --> 00:37:03,710
Yes,

449
00:37:05,150 --> 00:37:06,510
